            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 5131,
            "text": "{\"id\":\"msg_01FZNXBRtM1RHD1vytYuPMq9\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"model\":\"claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_017Eag4R9WbxZ7Vj2CiRP8xU\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"code\":\"import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from \\\"@/components/ui/card\\\";\\nimport { Rocket, Satellite, Telescope } from \\\"lucide-react\\\";\\n\\nexport const Features = () => {\\n  return (\\n    <section \\n      id=\\\"Features\\\" \\n      className=\\\"w-full py-16 bg-secondary\\\"\\n    >\\n      <div className=\\\"container mx-auto px-4\\\">\\n        {/* Header Section */}\\n        <div className=\\\"text-center mb-12\\\">\\n          <h2 className=\\\"text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-secondary-foreground\\\">\\n            Exploring the Cosmic Frontier\\n          </h2>\\n          <h3 className=\\\"text-xl mb-6 text-secondary-foreground-muted\\\">\\n            Transforming Humanity's Greatest Adventure into Tangible Progress\\n          </h3>\\n          <p className=\\\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-secondary-foreground-muted\\\">\\n            Space exploration represents more than technological achievement—it's a testament \\n            to human curiosity, innovation, and our collective potential to transcend known \\n            boundaries. Each mission expands our understanding of the universe and our place \\n            within it.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        {/* Features Grid */}\\n        <div className=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12\\\">\\n          {/* Advanced Spacecraft Technology */}\\n          <Card className=\\\"bg-background\\\">\\n            <CardHeader>\\n              <div className=\\\"flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 mb-4\\\">\\n                <Rocket className=\\\"h-6 w-6 text-primary\\\" />\\n              </div>\\n              <CardTitle className=\\\"text-background-foreground\\\">\\n                Advanced Spacecraft Technology\\n              </CardTitle>\\n            </CardHeader>\\n            <CardContent>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-background-foreground-muted\\\">\\n                Cutting-edge propulsion systems and materials that enable longer, safer \\n                journeys into deep space, pushing the boundaries of human exploration \\n                beyond previous limitations.\\n              </p>\\n            </CardContent>\\n          </Card>\\n\\n          {/* Satellite Observation Networks */}\\n          <Card className=\\\"bg-background\\\">\\n            <CardHeader>\\n              <div className=\\\"flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 mb-4\\\">\\n                <Telescope className=\\\"h-6 w-6 text-primary\\\" />\\n              </div>\\n              <CardTitle className=\\\"text-background-foreground\\\">\\n                Satellite Observation Networks\\n              </CardTitle>\\n            </CardHeader>\\n            <CardContent>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-background-foreground-muted\\\">\\n                Comprehensive global and interplanetary monitoring systems that provide \\n                unprecedented insights into planetary dynamics, climate patterns, and \\n                cosmic phenomena.\\n              </p>\\n            </CardContent>\\n          </Card>\\n\\n          {/* Interplanetary Research Platforms */}\\n          <Card className=\\\"bg-background\\\">\\n            <CardHeader>\\n              <div className=\\\"flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 mb-4\\\">\\n                <Satellite className=\\\"h-6 w-6 text-primary\\\" />\\n              </div>\\n              <CardTitle className=\\\"text-background-foreground\\\">\\n                Interplanetary Research Platforms\\n              </CardTitle>\\n            </CardHeader>\\n            <CardContent>\\n              <p className=\\\"text-background-foreground-muted\\\">\\n                Modular research stations designed to support extended missions, enabling \\n                scientific teams to conduct groundbreaking experiments in microgravity \\n                and extreme environments.\\n              </p>\\n            </CardContent>\\n          </Card>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        {/* CTA Section */}\\n        <div className=\\\"text-center\\\">\\n          <h4 className=\\\"text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-foreground mb-4\\\">\\n            Join the Cosmic Journey\\n          </h4>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  );\\n};\",\"summary\":\"Created a Features component for a space exploration landing page featuring three main cards highlighting Advanced Spacecraft Technology, Satellite Observation Networks, and Interplanetary Research Platforms. The component uses Shadcn UI Card components and Lucide icons, with semantic color utilities as specified in the theme guidelines. The layout is responsive and includes a header section with title, subtitle, and description, followed by a grid of feature cards and a CTA section.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":5128,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":1137,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
